{{Top|leg}}
'''Newest Coast Town''' was a colony on [[Ennth]]. It was destroyed by a massive thousand-[[Meter/Legends|meter]]-high [[Tsunami/Legends|tsunami]] caused by an [[Water/Legends|underwater]] [[Groundquake/Legends|groundquake]]. While 80% of the supplies in the [[City/Legends|city]] were saved, a few hundred [[colonists]] [[Death/Legends|died]], and two [[Starship/Legends|starships]] were lost.

